{"tid":2204564,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"民間研究指若推行「明日大嶼」或11年內耗盡儲備","createTime":"2020-09-16T06:48:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-16T09:32:03.000Z","uid":137088,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d0773f1334eb9f8046d250b66848414db25c0808","tid":2204564,"uid":137088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T06:48:05.000Z","msg":"陳樂謙報道<br />\n政府推出涉及240億元的第三輪「防疫抗疫基金」，又估計今個財政年度財赤會超過3000億元，財政儲備減至約8000多億元。<br />\n<br />\n有立法會議員建議政府發債推行「明日大嶼」計劃，又指計劃有助增加土地及房屋供應。<br />\n<br />\n有環保團體及經濟學者的研究指出，本港經濟面對內憂外患，政府如推行「明日大嶼」計劃，或會在11年內耗盡財政儲備。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1549874-20200916.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1549874-20200916.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=%2F2JumwqaKkMO2nYek6mTvd%2FmPfBwacFXLzUp2rw9Z8Q%3D&h=a7e85516\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1549874-20200916.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=b7172393\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1549874-20200916.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"2488b6c99235a9515987efd002aa2b5d8091dc7e","tid":2204564,"uid":172035,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T06:50:43.000Z","msg":"林鄭加速主義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nStrong hold定港樓都得啦"},{"pid":"3d283f861593c0552a22feff6c340e72acd7da3f","tid":2204564,"uid":277650,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T06:54:55.000Z","msg":"港共一起貪，唔洗咁耐吓話<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9148020b2d7d721e9c22ad7aee1b46b2fca053a3","tid":2204564,"uid":156579,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T06:58:12.000Z","msg":"支持林鄭<br />\n你班廢老公務員份長糧mola mola<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"